{"tid":1884363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蕭生突發！研究員實名揭露所長泄漏病毒","createTime":"2020-02-17T14:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T10:16:18.000Z","uid":209890,"like":526,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd280e89312e832a2c915054055eb8ac6c42925","tid":1884363,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ya4PzJm7kk0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYa4PzJm7kk0&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=2451aeb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ya4PzJm7kk0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MpfoT4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMpfoT4J.jpg&h=66358d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今獲中共你仲唔含家剷<br />\n全世界圍攻中共<br />\n成日話天滅中共<br />\n依獲天時地利人和齊晒<br />\n先有貿易戰<br />\n再黎陳同佳令香港人覺醒<br />\n再因為反送中令原本輸緊既英文贏埋台灣選舉戰<br />\n中共洗幾多錢都助攻唔到韓國條魚上位 , 依加仲要好快就會比高雄人趕走<br />\n之後美帝借香港打擊中共<br />\n再整一獲全世界都會圍倒中共既 生化武器自爆<br />\n最重要係有豬隊友助攻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊仲有4000億蝗蟲去緊中共呀<br />\n14億VS4000億 蝗蟲內戰<br />\n中國人絕對唔會餓死<br />\n佢地乜撚都食得架麻<br />\n蝗蟲好補架<br />\n蝗蟲食番蝗蟲咪岩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842ab933bae3ca318ec4859c89dc92112e5dfe57","tid":1884363,"uid":209890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"推爆<br />\n依單野要傳出去"},{"pid":"eaa2d16eeec3bd12f9dab233cb25ce44195ca595","tid":1884363,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cla